<view class="page page-themed-root">
  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">接单开关</view>

    <view class="row">
      <text class="row-text">开启接单状态</text>
      <view class="switch-shrink">
        <switch
          checked="{{settings.orderEnabled}}"
          data-key="orderEnabled"
          bindchange="onSwitchChange"
        ></switch>
      </view>
    </view>

    <text class="hint">
      关闭后，客户无法搜索到该模特，无法下单（进行中的订单不受影响）。
    </text>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">接单偏好</view>

    <view class="row">
      <text class="row-text">只接本地单</text>
      <view class="switch-shrink">
        <switch
          checked="{{settings.onlyLocal}}"
          data-key="onlyLocal"
          bindchange="onSwitchChange"
        ></switch>
      </view>
    </view>
    <text class="hint">基于城市一致的订单（当前仅做本地保存，后续对接城市匹配）。</text>

    <view class="row">
      <text class="row-text">只接女性客户</text>
      <view class="switch-shrink">
        <switch
          checked="{{settings.onlyFemale}}"
          data-key="onlyFemale"
          bindchange="onSwitchChange"
        ></switch>
      </view>
    </view>

  </view>

  <view class="btn-wrap">
    <button class="save-btn" bindtap="saveSettings">保存设置</button>
  </view>
</view>

